Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:18.58,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}There was a bird that could not fly any further than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:24.93,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}It scolded the sky with it's beautiful, perfect wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.74,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}"This place isn't too bad."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:30.57,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}"That sky isn't so high."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.61,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}"This place isn't good either."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:41.38,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}It feared the velocity it felt from its own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:48.34,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}Everyone has a chance... but no one can go further.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.05,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}"The truth is that it can't fly."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:53.96,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}"The truth is that it wants to fly."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:01:01.80,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}Right now, you are shining over by the wish it wants to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:07.25,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}Reflecting in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:13.09,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}"Standing in the future, always strong," that you is in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:19.15,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}Even though you are still shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:22.14,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,150)}But, if I reach out my hand with the same emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:29.95,OP2_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(150,400)}One day I'll grasp the real me, and become you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 60 seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just kill this bastard, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't turn back towards the light now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can do is accompany Kihara to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there with that shitty face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't you gonna save the brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey buddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're super cool or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You decide to stand up against an immense evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now you come here all alone, acting like the hero for this poor brat in distress...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can atone for your sins with just that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna eat dirt the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how much a life is worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who need to fall to hell are you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to bring that brat with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That disgusting right arm attached to your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that abomination of an angel you're protecting make me want to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be funny or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think your perspective is the only one that matters in this world? {OH THE IRONY}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ever try to accept others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate science!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detest it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate science for doing this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detest science for doing nothing to save my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what science gives birth to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're part of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell how disgusting it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's out of juice, he's just a piece of immobile garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You blasphemer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep calling myself misfortunate, but I have to say I'm pretty fortunate right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on, Kazakiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index is working on a way to save you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her friend, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, I'll take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop her no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwin' around, you little bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucking brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he can't use his power, my counter is also useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, killing him won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I need to do so he can't even die anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the original script of the virus I wrote in the brat's brain! {Apparently they still use SD cards in the future?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without this, the brat can never be saved! {Apparently, SD cards are made of glass now}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now? Pissed off, you little bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just crushed the thing you care about the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take anything back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time you start thinking about whether heaven exists or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vento stopped me from touching her hammer with my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I can destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem that I'll gain anything by fighting you close-quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have to worry about my surroundings, I can do as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sounds like you're having that monster help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't just sound like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as you'll get!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate God's Right Seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vento!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you worrying about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You science people set this entire thing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as that angel spawned, some kind of spell pressure was applied to the whole area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something similar to ruining the mana circulation in its area of effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aleister can come up with some bitter tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you continue to fight, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that cliché phrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... I couldn't dodge that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you need to be rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm a bit busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never relying on science again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother was killed by science.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was thanks to an attraction at an amusement park malfunctioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that it was perfectly safe, scientifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple safety mechanisms, a fully-automated speed control program...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made it sound like there was nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when it came down to it, none of that helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when we were brought to a hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they said that they didn't have enough blood for two transfusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that only one of us could be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So my brother told them, "Please save my sister."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, here I am, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of God's Right Seat fighting for such a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I detest science so much I'd even use God's Right Seat to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Science stole our future from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to diminish the Bible and our salvation with violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what the true nature of science is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only ever brings ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate and detest science.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If science has such a cold existence, then I'll destroy it and fill the world with one warmer!{law}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my duty to my brother, whose future I stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean science killed your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doctor didn't want him to die, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to save both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for the attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't built to hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was built to bring a smile to everyone's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother fully understood the situation he was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet he still wanted to save you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that sort of person would want you avenging him this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who wished for your happiness above all else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if a dying child's opinion is worth anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there wasn't enough blood, they should've given it to my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could've even used my own blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth something, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your brother's decision, you're standing here alive right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was its worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you of all people understand that the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'll find comfort in those words?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stole that child's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you say that if you were in his position?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I disagree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not living your life correctly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother made the ultimate sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to trample all over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to twist his sacrifice by saying he detested science until the very end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laughable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided this path in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you've done is heard my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can just sway me so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:15:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The danger that Academy City and Kazakiri are in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the hate Vento has for science...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to destroy all of those illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing compared to what your brother did, but I'll save you just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start you life over, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guy from earlier...{I'd say "the other day" but it looks like THE SUN HASN'T EVEN COME UP YET}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they related to all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of work here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is definitely the core of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically an angel construct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual formless Telesma has been forced into a container using a human image.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do at this point, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Short-hair, I've got a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Mikoto-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is this "electric brain-wave network"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's basically electric-based espers using each other's brain power in a single electromagnetic wave network.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this "AIM diffusion field spread throughout Academy City"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a natural field generated by all espers that permeates the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, basically, there's a special power filling the city, and this girl is its controller.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:17:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're harnessing the mind of this girl to distort the special power, which in turn created the angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I just need to unbind the shackles on this girl's mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how exactly do I go about doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A song?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get across easier than simple words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using rhythm and pitch, I can make multiple interactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is such a primitive method going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prayers are always heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save them with our prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all of Academy City!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you moving all the sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ki...hara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be boring if you went down so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the great service, Accelerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still pissed off at you, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna put you in a world of hurt before killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that hurts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Now I'm warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this a little more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those black wings on your back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of power is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he achieve another clearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What values did he put into his personal reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the true form of your power is an angel or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even noticed what's behind you, you monster.
