Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kazakiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:22:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I touch Kazakiri now, I'll destroy her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have business with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acqua of the Rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Vento, I am one of God's Right Seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to return for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Vento go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I let her go, and she were caught by the science side, she would be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already a piece of trash, destroyed by your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vento can't use Divine Punishment anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suppressed people will soon recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you've protected Academy City for now, so you needn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting me will only shorten your lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One fight has ended, but another unprecedented fight is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One that could be called a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Before the Battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross, the story begins.
